            <li>Diverges because <m>\displaystyle\lim_{a\to 0^+}\left[-1+\frac{1}{a}\right]</m> diverges.</li>
            <li>Converges because <m>\displaystyle\lim_{a\to 1^-}\left[-1+\frac{1}{a}\right]</m> converges.</li>
            <li>Diverges because <m>\displaystyle\lim_{a\to 1^-}\left[-1+\frac{1}{a}\right]</m> diverges.</li>
        </ol>
    </activity>
